OL,7,FAn assault that took place in a city
OL,8,Fcentre pub during celebrations is
OL,9,Fbeing treated as a , according to
OL,10,Fpolice.
OL,12,FA 23-year-old man has been arrested
OL,13,Ffollowing the incident at a pub in
OL,14,FHurst Street, near the Arcadian, on
OL,15,FFriday night (24 May).
OL,17,FPolice were called to the pub at
OL,18,Fapproximately 6pm where they were told
OL,19,Fthat a man had assaulted several
OL,20,Fpeople inside the venue and had left
OL,21,Fthe scene.
