OL,7,FFollowing a search through Birmingham
OL,8,Fcity centre, officers arrested a 23-
OL,9,Fyear-old man on suspicion of wounding
OL,10,Fand assault at approximately 7pm.
OL,11,FPolice say they are treating the
OL,12,Fincident as a hate crime.
OL,14,FThree men, aged 30, 31 and 34, are
OL,15,Fbelieved to have been assaulted and
OL,16,Ftheir injuries are not believed to be
OL,17,Fserious or life threatening.
OL,19,Fsays the assault happened during their
OL,20,Fpolicing and partner operation for
OL,21,FBirmingham Pride this weekend.
