OL,7,FChief Inspector Richard Evans, from
OL,8,FBirmingham police, said: "We will not
OL,9,Ftolerate hate crime in our city.
OL,11,F"People should be able to visit the
OL,12,Fcity without fear of being subjected
OL,13,Fto violence and threats.
OL,15,F"Planning for Pride takes place months
OL,16,Fin advance and the focus is to provide
OL,17,Fa highly visible presence around the
OL,18,FPride site, to make people feel safe
OL,19,Fand to prevent crime.
