OL,7,F"We take hate crime very seriously and
OL,8,Fwould encourage people to come forward
OL,9,Fif they've experienced a hate crime.
OL,11,F"While we'd prefer victims to come to
OL,12,Fus directly, we know that for a
OL,13,Fvariety of reasons, some people do not
OL,14,Fwant to speak with officers preferring
OL,15,Fto report crimes anonymously or not at
OL,16,Fall."
