OL,7,FIf you want to report the crime or
OL,8,Fincident to the police, it's a good
OL,9,Fidea to contact a hate crime support
OL,10,Fservice first. They can help you work
OL,11,Fout what to say in your report.
OL,13,FIf you don't want to talk to the
OL,14,Fpolice, you can ask an independent
OL,15,Forganisation to report it for you
OL,16,Fanonymously. These organisations are
OL,17,Fcalled 'third party reporting centres'.
OL,19,FIn an emergency, you should call 999.
